snippet.title: AFL Finals Fever gameplay (1996, PC)
snippet.description:
The high-res match early on is super laggy, but I think that might be just how this game plays lol because the timer is still in real time and the other gameplay vid of this game is super laggy too.

Most of the vid is in low-res mode, which plays far better, but this game isn't great.

Check out my main channel and other stuff at http://www.minimme.com/

:)
